<dl>
  <dt>Authors</dt>
  <dd>Samuel Drapeau, <a href="http://cms.uni-konstanz.de/math/kupper/">Michael Kupper</a> and <a href="">Ranja Reda</a></dd>
  <dt>Date</dt>
  <dd>2011</dd>
  <dt>Journal</dt>
  <dd>Advances in Mathematical Economics, 15:27-39</dd>
  <dt>Abstract</dt>
  <dd>We give robust representations of law-invariant monotone quasiconvex functions. The results are based on Jouini, Schachermayer and Touzi (2006) and Svindland (2010) showing that lawinvariant quasiconvex functions have the Fatou property.</dd>
  <dt>Keywords</dt>
  <dd>Fatou property, law-invariance, risk measure, robust representation</dd>
  <dt>Download</dt>
  <dd><a href="http://www.samuel-drapeau.info/downloads/DKR_LIRM1010.pdf" target="_blank"> pdf (open science)</a></dd>
